Toronto Blue Jays ended their six-game losing streak, 3-1 over the Texas Rangers
on Thursday night. Castillo hasn't lost since June 1. The right-hander allowed
just one run on four hits in seven innings. He struck out four and didn't walk a
batter.
</P>
